token_info.name: Prosopagnosia #01
token_info.description: "I can't remember her face, but when she looked at me, it felt like this."  Prosopagnosia is a neurological condition characterized by the inability to recognize faces. This is a GAN created by Adam Eivy (@antic) to capture the feeling of a look. Limited series in 512x512.
